dev/plans/runs/0.8.1-slice-30-option2-output.json:55:  "known_limitation": "FathomDB recall < naive_rag on memory classes because entity-node hits from graph/dense arms fall through to str(sh.id) doc_ids (no match) and push real doc nodes lower in RRF ranking. Root cause: ingest_with_extractor creates entity nodes but not source-doc nodes; two-pass ingest gives FTS hits with correct doc_ids, but graph/dense arms prefer entity nodes. Does not affect pipeline validation — all arms, ELPS harness, and gold loader work correctly.",
