dev/plans/runs/0.8.3-slice-5-output.json:24:      "detail": "Mem0-OSS is tractable within the footprint. The historical try_build()->None was (1) mem0ai not installed and (2) an unconfigured backend (default config targets OpenAI cloud + a Qdrant server). Both resolved by the pinned LOCAL config (airlock qwen3.6-27b + local bge-small + on-disk chroma). D0b first step = `pip install mem0ai chromadb sentence-transformers` (deliberately NOT run here to avoid polluting the shared .venv in this eval-infra slice). Residual risk: Mem0 add() runs one local-LLM extraction call per memory -> the slowest arm; mitigate by restricting Mem0 ingest to the gold-relevant LME sessions + run on the resilient harness. Conformance proven backend-free (fake in-memory backend)."
dev/plans/runs/0.8.3-slice-5-output.json:27:      "id": "power-target-underpowered-HITL",
dev/plans/runs/0.8.3-slice-5-output.json:29:      "detail": "The frozen power rule (paired MDE <= eps=0.05) is NOT achievable at feasible memory-class gold size. The Slice-5 unpaired variance proxy implies required N = factoid 524, knowledge_update 371, multi_session 768, temporal 752 -- all >> the provisional build target n_min=150 (LME caps real gold at ~130/class). n_min=150 makes the classes non-empty and comparable but is expected to remain UNDER-POWERED for a strict MDE<=eps paired parity claim. Slice 10 MUST run the real PAIRED power-check and, if mde>eps, escalate to HITL rather than claim parity (decision_rule_083 already encodes the underpowered:<class> guard). Surfaced now, not silently deferred."
dev/plans/runs/0.8.3-slice-5-output.json:59:  "next_step_for_orchestrator": "Cherry-pick the 3 commits (76bf9c75 design, 65f96ceb RED, 988aa499 GREEN) to main; run codex §9 review (corpus validity -- no vacuous/empty gold; eval-infra, not a product AC). Then Slice 10 (D0b priced parity), gated on the HITL Slice-0 sign-off (SIGNED): (1) install mem0ai+chromadb+sentence-transformers and stand up Mem0-OSS via mem0_local.build_local_mem0_config + stand up Graphiti/Zep; (2) consume the re-pin gold via R2Harness.from_repin_gold; (3) run the REAL paired power-check per class and ESCALATE to HITL on any mde>eps (the manifest implied-N proxy already shows all four classes need N>>150 -> expect under-power); (4) sanity-review the 48%-synthetic knowledge_update gold before citing its delta."
