dev/plans/runs/STATUS-0.8.1.md:828:**Problem statement (per Option 3 data):** Graph arm entity-node hits carry `SearchHit.id = canonical_nodes` integer row ID. The `doc_id_of` lambda in `FathomDBAdapter` resolves via `cursor_to_doc` (document write cursors only), so entity node hits fall through to `str(sh.id)` and never match gold `answer_session_ids`. Graph arm effect on all recall classes is ≤ 0 (temporal=0, multi_session=0, knowledge_update=-0.013, factoid=0).
