    21	
    22	## 1. The target (design §2/§4)
    23	
    24	Per memory class `c ∈ {factoid, knowledge_update, multi_session, temporal}`, the
    25	external gap `FathomDB − {mem0_oss, graphiti_zep, naive_rag}` on:
    26	- **(a) strict full-gold Recall@K** — LLM-free, $0. A query scores 1 iff *every*
    27	  `gold_doc_id` is in the arm's top-K (the existing `R2Harness.run` recall rule).
    28	- **(b) identical-answerer accuracy** — PRICED. One answerer / one prompt / one
    29	  context budget across all arms (the R2 invariant); reader `gpt-5.4` (temp0/seed0),
    30	  cheap-validate `gemini-flash-lite`.
    31	
