    33	m1 percentile helpers) and a per-class paired **MDE** (normal-approx
    34	`(z.975+z.80)·sd(dₚ)/√n`). The accuracy deltas feed `decide_083` → REACHED /
    35	NOT_REACHED + per-class gap + power verdict.
    36	
    37	## 2. Runner (`eval/d0b_parity_run.py`) — resilience first, before any spend
    38	
    39	Reuses `m1_verdict_run`'s proven mechanisms (do NOT hand-roll weaker ones):
    40	- **Atomic checkpoint** (`_atomic_write_json`: temp-file + `os.replace`) at least
    41	  every `checkpoint_every` (≤10) questions; the live checkpoint is never half-written.
    42	- **Auto-resume on by default** (`_resolve_resume`): the `<output>.checkpoint.json`
    43	  sidecar is detected automatically; a relaunch reuses every persisted `(qid,arm)`
    44	  cell (key-present incl. `None` = a real abstention, reused; absent = re-called) →
    45	  zero re-spend. Proven by a kill/restart unit test before any priced call.
    46	- **429/5xx backoff-and-recover**: the answerer is `CostTrackingAnswerer` (exponential
    47	  backoff over transient 429/5xx; a cell fails only after `max_retries`).
